<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> darẏnne niht / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> freuntſchaft in </ab>
