<ab><expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und Ulm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir lassen
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wissen, daz uns
                                                in geheim gesagt ist <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                wie daz nü in Francken grosz gewerb und
                                                  <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gewesen sey und
                                                dasselb volk sey die vordern naht bey naht ausz und
                                                hinauff gen <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geczogen,
                                                darnach wisz sich ewr
                                                  <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> czurihten und
                                                meldet <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> darynne niht;
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan> freuntschaft in den
                                                oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sachn</expan> lieb und
                                                  <expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan>, des
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig und
                                                  <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> das
                                                  <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii post
                                                  <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>can<ex>ta</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
